{"tid":2137533,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑男朋友好似帶左第二個上黎屋企","createTime":"2020-08-03T04:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T07:28:22.000Z","uid":12083,"like":12,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f0768a86dcd5872bf0219aad1c0a463f835e5d6f","tid":2137533,"uid":12083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"同男朋友就快二年 話說最近開始同佢搬左出去同居 咁我地當然仲好sweet啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算同居都無乜鬥交 一直都同佢好夾<br />\n<br />\n得閒就煮下飯仔 睇下戲 扑下野咁就一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都認定左佢係我終身伴侶 希望第時有機會可以同佢結婚咁<br />\n<br />\n呢排公司比較忙 所以成日都ot到好夜先番屋企 番到去男朋友都訓左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我見佢訓左我又未眼訓我就去洗衫呀 執下屋企野 做下家務咁<br />\n<br />\n就係咁比我發現到要洗果堆衫果到竟然有條女人底褲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同我男朋友有時為情趣都係有時著T-BACK互屌 無可能會有女人底褲<br />\n所以我懷疑我男朋友瞞住我帶左第二個上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我應唔應該同佢分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 仲好愛佢"},{"pid":"ea42f997d031010dd9e85596aeb9d7b54e08f2bf","tid":2137533,"uid":21355,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:13:49.000Z","msg":"分手啦屌你個死gay佬"},{"pid":"68824299af16a54db2e8e825c379c5884820cd00","tid":2137533,"uid":194326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"隱性gay"},{"pid":"990bf286a7dc7691d40f613780b988f543e7a876","tid":2137533,"uid":227971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:14:37.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.